    <header class="header">
        <div class="centered">
            <img src="images/Logos/logoOrangeCream.PNG" alt="Parklopedia Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-center">
        </div>
        <div class="hero">
 
            <div class="videoContainer">
            <video
            poster="images/GeneratedNationalPark.png"
            autoplay muted
            id="backgroundVideo">
                <source src="images/headerBackgrounds/auroraHeader.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
                Your Browser Does Not Support This Video.
            </video> 

        </div>
        </div>
    </header>

         <main id="main" class="main flex-column-center" tabindex="-1">

            <div class="blurBackground"> </div>
            <h2>Curious about park fees? <br>Wondering what amenities our park offers? <br>It's all here, right at your fingertips. </h2>
            <p>Our park information page is your gateway to adventure, offering a glimpse of the awe-inspiring landscapes that await you. Take a journey through stunning imagery, stay informed with real-time park alerts, and find all the necessary contact information for a seamless visit.

                And don't forget to check the current weather, ensuring you're fully prepared to make the most of your visit. </p>
                <h3>So, start exploring, and set yourself up to experience the great outdoors like never before!</h3>

    </main>


    <div class="customParkContent">
        <section class="imagesContainer">
            <div class="slideshow-container">

                <div class="mySlides">
                    <img src="" alt="Slideshow Image 1">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="prevNextBox flex-row">
            <button href="#" id="prevButton" class="prev">Previous</button>
            <button href="#" id="nextButton" class="next">Next</button>
        </div>
        </section>
        <div class="parkNameContainer">
            <div class="colorBackground"> </div>
    <h2 class="parkName" id="parkName"> Name Of Park </h2>
</div>
    <div class="container">

        <article id="parkInfoContainer" class="mainParkInformation">


            <section class="parkInfo" id="parkInfo">
                    <div class="parkDescriptionHeader" id="parkDescriptionHeader">
                <h3>Park Description: </h3>
                        </div>
                <p id="parkDescription" class="description"></p>
            </section>
            <section id="seasonalInfo" class="seasonalInfo">
                <div class="seasonalDescriptionHeader" id="seasonalDescriptionHeader">
                <h3>Seasonal Information: </h3>
                </div>
                <p id="weatherInfo"></p>
            </section>
            <div id="specialHours" class="specialHours">
                <div class="specialHoursDescriptionHeader" id="specialHoursDescriptionHeader">
                <h3>Special Operating Hours in Effect: </h3>
            </div>
                <p id="todaysOperatingHours"></p>
            </div>
            <section class="feeInfo" id="feeInfo">
                <div class="feesDescriptionHeader" id="feesDescriptionHeader">
                <h3>Entrance Fees: </h3>
                </div>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Type of Fee</th>
                            <th>Cost</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody id="feeInformation">

                    </tbody>
                </table>
                </section>
                <section class="npsButton" id="npsButton">
                <button class='npsPageButton'><a id="parkUrl" href="">Click here for the NPS entry on this
                        park.</a></button>
            </section>

        </article>
        <section class="weather">
            <div class="weatherHeader" id="weatherHeader">
                <h3>Weather</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="weatherContainer">
                <div class="currentTemp" id="currentTemp">
                    <img class="weatherImage" src="" alt="weatherImage">
                    <span class="temperature" id="temperature"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="highAndLowTemp">
                    <div class="maxTemp" id="maxTemp"></div>
                    <div class="minTemp" id="minTemp"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="threeDayForecastBox">
                <div class="datesBox"> </div>
                <div class="dateOne"></div>
                <div class="dateTwo"></div>
                <div class="dateThree"></div>

                <div class="weatherImgBox"> </div>
                <div class="weatherImgOne"> <img id="weatherImg1"></div>
                <div class="weatherImgTwo"><img id="weatherImg2"></div>
                <div class="weatherImgThree"><img id="weatherImg3"></div>

                <div class="highLowBox"> </div>
                <div class="highLowOne"></div>
                <div class="highLowTwo"></div>
                <div class="highLowThree"></div>


            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="contact"> This is how to contact the park, the hours are never. Contact info is just making bear
            noises into the night.</section>

    </div>

    <section class="alerts flex-column"> 
        <div class="alertsHeader" id="alertsHeader">
            <h3>Alerts: </h3> </div>
        <div class="alertsColorKey">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Alert Type</th>
                        <th>Color</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Danger</td>
                        <td style="background-color: #864622; color: #fff;">Dark Orange</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Caution</td>
                        <td style="background-color: #FFD580; color: #000;">Light Orange</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Information</td>
                        <td style="background-color: #90EE90; color: #000;">Green</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Park Closure</td>
                        <td style="background-color: #ADD8E6; color: #000;">Blue</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Other</td>
                        <td style="background-color: #fff; color: #000;">White</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="alertsInformationBox">
            
        </div>
        </div>
    </section>


